post_text:
Chromebook pickup information:
Students/parents should go to their respective buildings to pick up their Chromebooks. One Chromebook per family. If you have more than one child, go to the oldest child's building to pick up the shared Chromebook.

Please complete the approval form provided at this link (copy and paste) prior to picking up your child's Chromebook:
bit.ly/ovchromebook

Device Pickup will Take place this Friday, April 17th as follows:

Cardinal Elementary- 1:30 pm - 3:30 pm - at the Main Entrance;

Orchard View Early Elementary- 11:00 am - 1:00 pm in the Front Bus Loop;

Middle School - 10:30 am - 12:30 pm - Front Bus Loop;

High School - 1:30 pm - 3:30 pm - Main Entrance (West Side of the Building)

